First start from kafka folder in first cmd propmt
  zookeeper-server-start.bat config\zookeeper.properties

second start kafka server for first broker in second cmd propmt
  kafka-server-start.bat config\server.properties

Create a new topic with 3 partitions with one broker(replication factor) in third cmd propmt
  kafka-topics.bat --zookeeper localhost:2181 --create --topic My_First_Sample_App --partitions 3 --replication-factor 1

Check the list and details of the topic in third cmd propmt
  kafka-topics.bat --zookeeper localhost:2181 --list
  kafka-topics.bat --zookeeper localhost:2181 --topic My_First_Sample_App --describe

Delete the topic  in third cmd propmt
  kafka-topics.bat --zookeeper localhost:2181 --topic My_First_Sample_App --delete

Create a producer in third cmd propmt
  kafka-console-producer --broker-list localhost:9092 --topic My_First_sample_App
  
 Create a Consumer in fourth cmd propmt
  kafka-console-consumer --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --topic My_First_sample_App
  
Create a group for consumer in many cmd propmt's
  kafka-console-consumer --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --topic My_First_sample_App --group My_First_Group
